title: Dua Lipa - Training Season (2024)
description: In the "Training Season" video, Dua Lipa remains composed at a cafe, surrounded by gawking men taking photos of her. The song's inspiration, as shared by Lipa, stemmed from a series of bad dates, leading her to declare the end of her "training season" and shaping the song with songwriters Caroline Ailin and Tobias Jesso Jr.
